result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="用户名"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'username',
          {
            rules:[
              { required: true, message: '请输入用户名' },
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.username : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="新密码"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="password"
        v-decorator="[
          'password',
          {
            rules: [
              { required: true, message: '请输入新密码' },
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' },
              {validator:validatePassword , message: '密码格式不正确'},
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.password : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="新密码确认"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="password"
        placeholder=""
        v-decorator="[
          'retry_password',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' },
              {validator:validateSortPsw , message: '密码再次输入不正确'},
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.retry_password : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
